TY  - JOUR
TI  - A Test for the Presence of First-Order Vector Autoregressive Errors when Lagged Endogenous Variables are Present
AU  - Guilkey, David K.
AB  - [This paper derives an asymptotically valid test for first-order autoregressive errors. The test is derived in a simultaneous system of equations context, and allows lagged endogenous variables to be present in the model.]
